* Perrin, W. F., B. Würsig, and J. G. M. Thewissen (2002) &quot;Encyclopedia of Marine Mammals&quot;. San Diego: Academic Press.
* Riedman, M. (1990) &quot;The Pinnipeds: Seals, Sea Lions and Walruses&quot;. Berkeley: University of California Press.

