<doc id="46137" wikidata="Q7282119" url="?curid=46137" title="Rafael E. Núñez">
<text>Rafael E. Núñez is a professor of cognitive science at the University of California, San Diego and a proponent of embodied cognition. He co-authored &quot;Where Mathematics Comes From&quot; with George Lakoff.

